<section id="parameters" class="section">

<h2>Configuration Parameters</h2>

<p class="section-note">
Configuration values that can influence connection pressure, memory spills, vacuum lag, WAL pressure, and parallel query behavior.
</p>

<details open>

<summary>
Connections
</summary>

<table>

<tr>
<th>Parameter</th>
<th>Value</th>
</tr>

{% for row in parameters.connections %}

<tr>
<td>{{ row.name }}</td>
<td>{{ row.setting }} {{ row.unit }}</td>
</tr>

{% endfor %}

</table>

</details>

<details open>

<summary>
Memory
</summary>

<table>

<tr>
<th>Parameter</th>
<th>Value</th>
